  <h2>Sonuç</h2>
  <p>Deprem, ne zaman olacağı bilinemeyen ancak sonuçları öngörülebilir bir doğa olayıdır. Paniği önlemenin ve zararı en aza indirmenin tek yolu bilinçli bir hazırlıktan geçer. Bugün ayıracağınız birkaç saatlik çaba, yarın sizin veya sevdiklerinizin hayatını kurtarabilir. Deprem çantanızı hazırlamayı ertelemeyin.</p>

  <Fragment slot="en">
  <p>Turkey's location on active fault lines makes living with the reality of earthquakes — and being prepared at all times — a necessity. Experts emphasize that the <strong>first 72 hours (the Golden Hours)</strong> after a potential disaster are the most critical period for survival. Rescue teams may not be able to reach every area immediately. This is exactly why a pre-prepared, accessible, and complete "Earthquake Kit" (Emergency Kit) becomes the most important shield protecting you and your family.</p>

  <h2>What Is an Earthquake Kit and Why Is It Necessary?</h2>
  <p>An earthquake kit is a portable emergency kit designed to meet your basic survival needs after a major tremor — whether you have safely evacuated your building or find yourself trapped in debris. After a disaster, electricity, water, natural gas, and communication lines can be cut. Stores and pharmacies may be closed or inaccessible. The supplies in your kit maximize your chances of survival during the critical window before help arrives.</p>

