    <p>The next step after preparing your kit is knowing when and how to use it: our <a href="/blog/deprem-sonrasi-ilk-24-saat.html">first 24 hours after an earthquake roadmap</a> walks through the entire process from evacuation to shelter, step by step.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Conclusion</h2>
  <p>An earthquake is a natural event whose timing cannot be known, but whose consequences can be anticipated. The only way to prevent panic and minimize harm is through informed preparation. A few hours of effort today can save your life — or the lives of those you love — tomorrow. Don't delay preparing your earthquake kit.</p>
